                                 <item>IV: fols. 25-32 (25+32, 26+31, 27+30. 28+29) </item>
                                 <item>V: fols. 33-40 (33+40, 34+39, 35+38, 36+37) </item>
                                 <item>VI: fols. 41-48 (41+48, 42+47, 43+46, 44+45) </item>
                                 <item>VII: fols. 49-56 (49+56, 50+55, 51+54, 52+53)</item>
                                 <item>VIII: fols. 57-64 (57+64, 58+63, 59+62, 60+61) </item>
                                 <item>IX: fols. 65-73 (65+73, 66+72, 67+71, 68+70, 69) [Fol. 69 is
                                    a small slip.]</item>
                                 <item>X: fols. 74-81 (74+81, 75+80, 76+79, 77+78) </item>
                                 <item>XI: fols. 82-89 (82+89, 83+88, 84+87, 85+86) </item>
