                              other pages.</p></condition>
                     </supportDesc>

                     <layoutDesc>
                        <layout columns="1" writtenLines="20 23">
                           <p>
                              <list>
                                 <item>The text is written in one column with 20-23 lines per page
                                    and 7-12 words per line.</item>
                                 <item>The written area measures ca. <dimensions type="written">
                                       <height unit="mm" quantity="160">160</height>
                                       <width unit="mm" quantity="120">120</width>
                                    </dimensions>.</item>
