                        Kålund dates it to the <origDate notBefore="1650" notAfter="1699">second
                           half of the seventeenth century</origDate>
                        (<bibl><ref target="KKKat">Katalog</ref>
                           <biblScope unit="volume">II</biblScope>, <biblScope unit="pages"
                              >290</biblScope></bibl>).</p>
                  </origin>
                  <provenance>
                     <p>According to the AM-slip, <name type="person" key="ArnMag001">Árni
                           Magnússon</name> had this manuscript from <name type="person"
                           key="PalJon005">Páll Vídalín</name> who had acquired it from <name
                           type="place">Vigur</name>.</p>
                  </provenance>
               </history>
